{"id":"7658","name":"Prepare The Car","tagline":"A Shortcut to prepare your selected Tesla before you set off","icon":"ios14 c4282601983 g59854","latest":"23481","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This Shortcut will prepare your car for you when you are soon to set off. It has setup variables which you configure for what temperature to set the HVAC to depending on whether it is \"hot\" or \"cold\" outside, and at what outside temperature you consider it to be \"hot\".</p>\n<p>It will also bump the charge limit up slightly if your car is currently plugged in to help warm the battery, and it will warm the car an extra degree if the weather forecasts snow.</p>\n<p>Running the Shortcut when the HVAC is already running will turn the HVAC off again, if you wish to \"cancel\" going out.</p>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.0 - Dec. 3, 2020, 3:22 p.m.</strong></p><p>First public version.</p>"}